---

<BaseLayout>
  <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-8 lg:py-12">
    <header>
      <Text
        tag="h1"
        variant="display5XL"
        class="font-bold leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter uppercase"
      >
        Just fucking<br />use Astro
      </Text>
      <Text
        tag="p"
        variant="textLG"
        class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-muted-foreground"
      >
        (Unless you're building an actual app, you sweet, fragile,
        over-engineering dipshit motherfucker.)
      </Text>
    </header>

    <div class="mt-12 text-sm leading-relaxed divide-y divide-border">
      {
        content.map((item) => (
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-12 gap-y-4 py-8 ">
            <Text
              tag="p"
              variant="textLG"
              class="text-balance font-medium tracking-tight"
            >
              {item.label}
            </Text>
            <div class="text-muted lg:col-span-2 ">
              {item.text && (
                <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" set:html={item.text} />
              )}
              {item.items && (
                <div class={item.text ? "mt-2 " : ""}>
                  {item.items.map((listItem) => (
                    <Text
                      tag="p"
                      variant="textBase"
                      set:html={`— ${listItem}`}
                    />
                  ))}
                </div>
              )}
              {item.suffix && (
                <Text
                  tag="p"
                  variant="textBase "
                  class="mt-3"
                  set:html={item.suffix}
                />
              )}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <Text
        tag="h2"
        variant="display4XL"
        class="font-bold text-balance leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter uppercase"
      >
        Now go ship something fast, asshole.
      </Text>
      <Text tag="p" variant="textLG" class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-muted">
        If you're building a mostly-content website and still reaching for a
        full SPA like a fucking amateur: you're not being advanced, dipshit.
        You're being lazy, insecure, and shit at trade-offs like the incompetent
        motherfucker you are.
      </Text>
      <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-muted">
        Go build something that loads fast, ships less JavaScript, and doesn't
        actively hate your users, you piece of shit. Now fuck off and code.
      </Text>
    </section>

    <footer class="mt-12 leading-relaxed">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-x-12 py-3 border-t border-border"
      >
        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-muted tracking-tight"
          >Inspirations</Text
        >
        <div>
          <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-muted">
            Also: if you want the fucking vibe, these were the obvious goddamn
            inspirations, you curious bastard:
          </Text>
          <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside w-full">
            {
              inspirations.map((link) => (
                <li>
                  <Text tag="span" variant="textSM" class="text-muted">
                    <a
                      href={link.url}
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noopener"
                      class="underline hover:no-underline text-foreground"
                    >
                      {link.name}
                    </a>
                    — {link.desc}
                  </Text>
                </li>
              ))
            }
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <Text
        tag="p"
        variant="textBase"
        class="text-muted py-3 border-t border-border"
      >
        Now stop reading and go fucking build something, asshole.
      </Text>
    </footer>
  </Wrapper>
</BaseLayout>
